Iowa school districts boundaries maintained by the Iowa Department of Education. This boundary layer represents legal school district boundaries, where possible. Efforts to adjust boundaries to match legal boundary descriptions is ongoing.Â This dataset is updated at least annually, or as needed. Last update - 2/25/2019
